Campaign Inclusion Report Install Instructions
-------------------------------------------
1. After installing, access the new Campaign Inclusion Report
application and click on the "Campaign Report Headers" Tab.
2. Create a new Campaign Report Header object and click continue.
3. Now you will see the report screen.
Here, you can choose whether to search on leads, contacts, or both.
You can search whether a campaign member was included in a campaign
with a certain status, or excluded from a campaign.  You can do this
for multiple campaigns.

You can either choose to save your search terms, save your search
terms and results, or save your results as campaign members to a
campaign.
4. If you choose to save your search terms, you can re-run your report at any time by clicking the "Run Report" button on your Campaign Report Header object.


